  "commute": "From HKG airport, the SkyPier ferry runs straight to Shekou Cruise Center (~30 min, ~HKD 299 / ¥280), and you stay airside with no HK immigration (luggage through-checked), then ~5 min taxi to the apartment. 11 sailings/day. HKG→Shekou: 08:15, 09:45, 11:00, 13:00, 15:00, 16:00, 17:00, 18:00, 19:00, 20:00, 21:15. Shekou→HKG: 07:15, 08:45, 10:00, 12:00, 14:00, 15:00, 16:00, 17:00, 18:00, 19:00, 20:15. Buy ≥60 min before sailing; for an onward HK flight allow ~3 h. Verify times on cmskchp.com (holidays vary). Alternative: high-speed rail HK West Kowloon → Futian (~14 min), then Metro Line 2/12 to Sea World."
